# Licences — Triple Memory

This repository follows the T(h)reehouse +EC Corporate Design blueprint
§0.3 split-licence architecture. Different layers of the project carry
different licences. See the licence applicable to the specific layer you
are using — do not assume a uniform licence across the repository.

## Layer matrix

| Layer | Content | Licence | SPDX | Details |
|-------|---------|---------|------|---------|
| Code & tooling | Engine source (HTML, CSS, JS), build scripts | MIT | `MIT` | [full text below](#mit-licence-code--design-assets) |
| Design assets | `assets/cd/*`, `packs/geography/icons/*.svg` | MIT | `MIT` | same MIT grant; see also upstream licence at [cd-rules][cd-rules] |
| Frameworks & data | `docs/*` (blueprints, task cards, research, interface schemas), `packs/geography/*.json`, `packs/geography/CURATION_STATEMENT.md` | CC BY-SA 4.0 | `CC-BY-SA-4.0` | see [`LICENCE-CONTENT`](LICENCE-CONTENT) |
| Fonts | IBM Plex Mono, Crimson Pro (loaded from Google Fonts) | SIL OFL 1.1 | `OFL-1.1` | governed by upstream; not redistributed here |

Per-folder notes live in each folder's README where applicable.

[cd-rules]: https://github.com/threehouse-plus-ec/cd-rules

